;Process Start-up------------------------------------------
N230 M56			; Escolha de fibra (confirmar)
N240 G4F4			;
N241 M78			; Shielding Gas ON!!!!!!!!!!
N250 M0				;

;Powder supply-----------------------------------------

N270 M62			; Mixer de pó ON
